Reference

Datasets

Datasets packed within the package, most lists with codes.

ciselnik_CSU

data.frame linking codes of CSU to RUIAN codes

katastralni_uzemi

data.frame of all cadastral territories in Czech Republic

kraje

data.frame of all regions(NUTS3) in Czech Republic

obce

data.frame of all settlements in Czech Republic

okresy

data.frame of all districts (LAU1) in Czech Republic

orp

data.frame of all settlements of type III (orp) in Czech Republic

pou

data.frame of all settlements of type II (pou) in Czech Republic

ČÚZK

Functions related to datasets from State Administration of Land Surveying and Cadastre.

load_Data200() save_Data200() load_Data200_info()

Load or save from Data200

load_Data50() save_Data50() load_Data50_info()

Load or save from Data50

generate_Data200_citation() generate_Data50_citation()

Generate attribution for dataset Data50 od Data200

load_RUIAN_settlement()

Extract data from RUIAN

load_RUIAN_state()

Extract data from RUIAN for whole Czech Republic

load_cadastral_territory()

Extract data from Cadastral map

ČSÚ

Functions related to datasets from Czech Statistical Office.

load_SLDB_2011() load_SLDB_2011_col_explanations()

Get information from Czech census in 2011

load_population_age() load_population_age_col_explanations()

Load population by age

load_population_settlements() load_population_settlements_col_explanations()

Load populations from settlements
